Dialogue: 2,0:00:35.86,0:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks to these pictures you took...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:38.31,0:00:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The Guitar Fighters' popularity has gone down.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:41.62,0:00:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.52,0:00:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You really stabbed them in the back, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Aren't you afraid that their spirits will come back to haunt you?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.86,0:00:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If I was afraid of ghosts...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wouldn't be in this line of work.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:54.49,0:00:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, what do you want \Nfrom me, Mr. Superstitious?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:58.87,0:01:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I want some new faces.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:01.41,0:01:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If we have no scoops, \Nour weekly pictorials won't sell.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.83,0:01:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, how about this girl?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:07.21,0:01:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Our next target, huh? {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:01:10.13,0:01:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:01:11.75,0:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A sixteen year old idol who debuted recently.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.34,0:01:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But, her real name and her background information are unknown to the public. {data sounds weird, even though it was used here}
Dialogue: 2,0:01:19.72,0:01:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:20.81,0:01:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon{\i0}, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Alright, alright! You're listening to Radio Name!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:28.23,0:01:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Next, we have a question \Nby Furuta Muntaro-kun.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:30.06,0:01:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}"Full Moon-san, what kind of \Nartist do you want to be?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:01:34.53,0:01:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's what it says...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:35.82,0:01:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So, how about it?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.90,0:01:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you have any goals?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:38.87,0:01:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, well...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:43.49,0:01:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, for now, I just want to keep on singing...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:46.04,0:01:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and keep on sending my feelings.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:49.63,0:01:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sending your feelings?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:50.75,0:01:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you singing for someone special?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:52.80,0:01:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:55.26,0:01:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's...  {naisho}
Dialogue: 2,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's a secret.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:59.34,0:02:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A secret, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:01.30,0:02:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}By the way, {\i1}Full Moon-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:02:02.72,0:02:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How about your real name?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, right, that's also a secret.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm, I see. {hmmm? was it kept intentionally, thet third "m"}
Dialogue: 2,0:02:08.98,0:02:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everything is a secret, huh?
