Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.02,0:03:33.31,BackwardLetters,,0,0,0,Sign,{\be1\fad(714,0)\bord0.25\frx348\fry182\frz26.09\c&H0000FF&\3c&H05086D&\fscx183\fscy156\pos(336.577,304.143)}Lens. {Backward red text}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.24,0:03:46.95,BackwardLetters,,0,0,0,Sign,{\bord0.15\c&H7A78F8&\3c&H040788&\fscx153\fscy131\pos(362.74,343.643)}Lens. {Normal, needs blur to match}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.64,0:03:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Lens? {Meroko's tone says there should be a ?}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He's really persistent.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If he keeps this up, I won't be able to drop you off, Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is kinda scary.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:58.32,0:03:58.92,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right. {Shani: Did Takuto actually want to kill that guy there? lol. He is a shinigami after all. :D}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:12.37,0:04:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Damn it! {Even scumbags abide by the law}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:14.82,0:04:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Looks like we lost him.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.11,0:04:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Saegusa won't let you go that easily once he targets you.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.02,0:04:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just like a hyena.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:22.04,0:04:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There is no celebrity who can get away once he sets his eyes on them. {edited: singular, also, them should remain them}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:25.60,0:04:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But, I don't have anything for him to aim at. {Sadly, you kinda do}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:29.12,0:04:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki, you haven't said your real name, or profile in public, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.92,0:04:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}For a guy like him, that's like hitting the jackpot.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:37.61,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That can't be...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:38.97,0:04:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:39.86,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If anything happens, everyone in the office will do anything to protect you.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You aren't alone.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:46.05,0:04:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Right.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you for the ride.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.11,0:04:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:55.39,0:04:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:56.03,0:04:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Maybe I should take you to your house?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No, that's all right.{}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:00.55,0:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:02.41,0:05:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, if anything happens, contact me immediately, okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:08.12,0:05:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If anyone finds out my real name, I might not be able to sing anymore.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll make sure that'll never happen.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, whatever you do, don't look behind you.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:19.28,0:05:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:21.93,0:05:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're being followed.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}W-Why?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Looks like we didn't lose him.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:27.10,0:05:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh no, what should I do?{}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.81,0:05:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just keep walking like normal.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:31.61,0:05:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Turn at the corner.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is bad.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't change you back in this situation.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:53.72,0:05:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No way...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.26,0:06:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, over there!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Go underground from there!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.73,0:06:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There, everything's fine now.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:23.55,0:06:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's go.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:29.58,0:06:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's him.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Like I said, everything was fine, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.88,0:06:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:56.38,0:06:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... I was scared. {}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:59.02,0:07:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:00.78,0:07:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sounds like trouble.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:03.04,0:07:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But, Takuto helped me out so I got away.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:06.81,0:07:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, I have to get up early tomorrow.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:10.02,0:07:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I am off to take a bath. {missing line?}
Dialogue: 2,0:07:13.70,0:07:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What is it, Meroko?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:20.18,0:07:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I couldn't say it in front of her.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:23.34,0:07:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We have a new task.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:25.16,0:07:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Does this have something to do with delaying her death?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:27.61,0:07:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm, what's this?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The letters are backwards.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Right.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.09,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Backwards means they're the opposite of the usual pattern.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:35.45,0:07:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In other words, it's not something that will delay her death.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:38.94,0:07:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's something that will bring \Nabout her death sooner.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:42.20,0:07:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Bring about her death sooner?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's "Lens".
Dialogue: 2,0:07:47.04,0:07:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}"Lens?"
Dialogue: 2,0:07:50.15,0:07:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That Saegusa guy's camera?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:53.45,0:07:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It'd be best for her to take a break from work tomorrow.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:56.83,0:07:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:57.93,0:07:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can take on that bastard myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's no use.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:00.76,0:08:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're still new at this.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:02.47,0:08:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's absolutely impossible!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:04.31,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then, what are you planning on doing?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is this really gonna work?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:18.20,0:08:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... this is the only thing we can do.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:20.99,0:08:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This, and this, and this...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:22.94,0:08:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, this one too.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A dream, huh?{}
Dialogue: 2,0:08:33.55,0:08:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No, it's not a dream!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:34.77,0:08:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you doing, Meroko?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:37.50,0:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, well, I... {Identity theft}{Shani: Bunny ears! Meroko <3}
Dialogue: 2,0:08:39.50,0:08:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I just wanted to try going out \Nas {\i1}Full Moon {\i0} today.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:43.52,0:08:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.30,0:08:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I just thought that you should take a break every now and then.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.39,0:08:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Your job is tough, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:52.49,0:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I like my job.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry to say this... {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:08:54.89,0:08:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm doing my job, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm, your job?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.61,0:09:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No, it's all right, Meroko.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Looks like you're going to stay home.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:04.85,0:09:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...{it was my perfect opportunity to finally go out and have some fun myself. You and Mitsuki are always having all the fun; while I have to act the obedient girl in her place! T_T BEEEEDA! XP}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:05.90,0:09:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll definitely protect her.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong with Meroko?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, let's hurry.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.50,0:09:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay. {Timing issue}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:28.51,0:09:29.63,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Whatever happens...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.49,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:49.27,0:09:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay. Good job!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:52.53,0:09:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh? You were followed by that Saegusa?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:55.39,0:09:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah... it was such a bother.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We had the same problem.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:00.80,0:10:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks to him... one of our \Nstaff members had to quit.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:03.83,0:10:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really, he is such a bother.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mission accomplished!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, that's all for today then.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:13.93,0:10:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:15.21,0:10:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How about a ride? {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:10:18.89,0:10:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nope, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:20.51,0:10:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, be careful on your way home.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:24.25,0:10:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll be leaving then.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:30.78,0:10:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-san worries a lot, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:33.16,0:10:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.11,0:10:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Although we haven't seen \Nthat bastard Saegusa yet.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.29,0:10:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:41.03,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um... you're {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Can we take a picture with you?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:48.00,0:10:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Uh, s-sure.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.37,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Smile for us, 'kay?{not sync}
Dialogue: 2,0:10:52.23,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Get a bit closer.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay, I'm taking one now.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.13,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yay!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Say "cheese."
Dialogue: 2,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:58.84,0:10:59.90,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We're gonna cheer for you.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:00.60,0:11:02.32,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-Thanks.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.10,0:11:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez, I got all worked up for nothing.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, that surprised me.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:08.87,0:11:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I thought it was that Saegusa again...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:14.70,0:11:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's him!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:16.25,0:11:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's go!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}O-Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:24.49,0:11:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Damn!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:25.53,0:11:29.60,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If my secret is uncovered, \Nthen I can't sing anymore. {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:30.04,0:11:32.25,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And if that happens, Eichi-kun... {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:34.63,0:11:35.89,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}It's no use. {more blur edge}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.89,0:11:37.49,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}You're still new at this.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:37.49,0:11:39.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3\fad(0,250)}It's absolutely impossible!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.17,0:11:41.76,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You think that's gonna stop me?!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:42.89,0:11:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, what are you doing?! {and he was stopped right there, LOL}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:44.55,0:11:45.85,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:49.44,0:11:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}At this rate, he'll catch up to us.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:56.65,0:11:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh? W-W-Wait!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:00.16,0:12:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When we get the chance, I'll turn you back into a 12-year-old!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}O-Okay.
