Dialogue: 2,0:12:12.63,0:12:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You can hide over there!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:15.79,0:12:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hurry up!
