Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:50.28,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,100)}Why... just why have I fallen in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:56.75,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\be3\fad(200,200)}Yet, still... I can't stop my tears from falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:27.78,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(166,100)}I lost way too much back then
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:32.04,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}I couldn't sing at all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:36.54,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,100)}That place you had to leave for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:44.13,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,0)}It happened to be the place where I was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:50.52,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,100)}On that day I could see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:55.35,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,0)}The desolation lying in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:21:00.94,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}I wonder if it's the same for both of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:08.37,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}If you would just notice, I'm always by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:14.41,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,0)}Why do I love you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:20.42,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,0)}Your voice is calling out with such sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:26.51,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,0)}I never knew what was supporting me, back then, and even now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:33.06,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,840)}Until we became so far apart...
